Edith Peters https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edith_Peters 0 Edith Peters (April 14, 1926 – October 28, 2000) was an American singer and actress. She appeared in more than sixteen films from 1957 to 1981. Edith_Peters ( April_14_,_1926 – October_28_,_2000 ) was an_American_singer_and_actress .
